FT  19 FEB 92 / Man on BCCI charge is bailed
A BUSINESSMAN charged in connection with the closure of BCCI was yesterday
released on bail of Pounds 200,000 plus Pounds 400,000 sureties. Mr Mohammed
Baqi is charged with falsely informing BCCI's auditor that a company owed
the bank more than Dollars 76m (Pounds 42.9m).
